    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "After doesn't leak a goroutine in the sense that it can be garbage collected now, but that doesn't mean it wouldn't cause the leak detector to trigger. If the context expires before the timer fires, the After goroutine could continue running after the test completes.\r\n\r\nMaybe I'm wrong on that but the docs don't seem to disagree.",
    "commit_id": "6e756b44ae6191c3487cba7c33cb7284974a412c",
    "created_at": "2025-10-16T05:56:14Z",
